snippet.title: Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer ft. Elvish Yadav, Nikhil Vijay, Malhaar Rathod | Amazon MX Player
snippet.description:
Amazon MX Player presents 
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer

Starring: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna
Production House: Rusk Studios
Produced By: Rusk Media Pvt. Ltd.
Directed By: Tanmai Rastogi
Developed, Story, Screenplay and Written by: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romance
 
About Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, a small-town boxer from Safidon, enters Delhi‚Äôs elite St. Collins college to fulfill his brother‚Äôs dream of becoming a polished, English-speaking graduate. Amidst bullies, culture shocks, and class divides, he falls for Antara Shukla ‚Äî a senior with political aspirations and far out of his league. When a humiliating dare collides with his growing feelings and a family crisis back home, Rajveer must fight harder than ever ‚Äî this time, not for glory, but for love, dignity, and survival.

About Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is India‚Äôs leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. With a strong focus on original content, Amazon MX Player has launched some of the largest shows in India, which includes Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Who‚Äôs your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter ‚Äì Totega Nahi Todega and more. Amazon MX Player also offers a rich selection of international content dubbed in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu under MX Vdesi, featuring popular shows like What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, and more!

Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. The inspiration behind this video: 

Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. While Hopper and Joyce are helping Eleven train, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, and Robin coordinate ways to locate Vecna. Max is still present, but she remains in a coma, serving as a reminder about how high the stakes are.

The inspiration behind this video: 

Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. While Hopper and Joyce are helping Eleven train, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, and Robin coordinate ways to locate Vecna. Max is still present, but she remains in a coma, serving as a reminder about how high the stakes are.

snippet.title: 4 AADMI (Official Music Video) | Sumit Parta | Mr.Maxxx | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Mahra Tora presents the official music video of 4 Aadmi by Sumit Parta & Mr.Maxxx. It is a powerful Haryanvi track full of energy, emotion, and real-life hustle. 4 Aadmi celebrates confidence, struggle, and the moment when doubters finally start giving respect. It‚Äôs an anthem for every youngster chasing dreams and proving their worth through hard work.

üéß Listen to 4 Aadmi on all audio stores:-

‚ô™ Spotify - https://bfan.link/4-aadmi/spotify

‚ô™ Apple - https://bfan.link/4-aadmi/appleMusic

‚ô™ Gaana - https://bfan.link/4-aadmi/gaana

‚ô™ Amazon Music - https://bfan.link/4-aadmi/amazonMusic

‚ô™ YouTube Music - https://bfan.link/4-aadmi/youtubeMusic

‚ô™ Jio Saavn - https://bfan.link/4-aadmi/jiosaavn

Credits:-
Song - 4 Aadmi
Singer - Sumit Parta & Mr. Maxxx
Music - Mr Maxxx
Lyrics - Sumit Parta
Video - Jerry Batra
DOP - Artur Styan 
Second Dop - Vahe 
Edit/Grade -  Raj Ghumaan
Line Production - Ok Report
Dop Assist - Henrik Karapetyan
Gafer¬†-¬†Xcho
Publicity Design -  Uncanny Designs

For More Updates, Subscribe to: https://www.youtube.com/@mahratoraharyanvi
 
Also You Can:
'LIKE' us on Facebook: 
https://www.facebook.com/mahratora
 
FOLLOW' us on Instagram: 
https://www.instagram.com/mahratora

Lyrics:-
Choro hada m bitha de chot
Bakri tu koni goat
Vair koni ghale yaar
Dekh k n kadi thoth
Jealousy na rakhu jadi
Moj me hi reu roj
Chahe khali ho ya bhari revo
Mero goj
Choro winner hai
Mehngo khave dinner hai
Part time punya kare
Full time sinner hai
Feelings inner hai
Rap game k mha
Choro jadu kre jiya witcher hai
Truth bitter hai
Log side switcher hai
Jo sath khaya piya be hi
Yaar sala snitcher hai
Dhue m uda ryo yaar sari fikar hai
Thadi mehfila me chale mero hi jikar hai
kon jle kon tle mera dhyan koni
Golibaji ala mne gyaan koni
Goli awe h chlani che bnda marwalo
Me normal banda bhgwan koni
Lagi jaat gail yaari aag dewe ge
Yaar Baniye b goli re chla dewe ge
Mehnga rakhna b howe  hatiyar lajmi
Mhari sangat me bnja khukhar admi
Re ghnta fark ni bole k ye 4 admi
Bs door rho pka me bekar admi
Khuli ankhya te hi dekhra hu bde sapne
Kad chain te tah soya mere khud yaad ni
Chiye range rover pura hangover
Nind kachi paki Chiye hot shawer
Ghadi Rm ki dhila dhila lower
Sale ve kiu chidee jo mne mile koni
mere personal kise gelya gile koni
Me to Bina dekhe mar deu  teer target pe
Ve Dhyan lake mare par pile konya
Re ghar k upar jhaj uda du
Sidha bhidle khaaj mita du
sir pe jonsa taj hta du
Satranga koi baaj bna du
Jit jit lagi lihaj mita du
Ban financer  viyaj bitha du
kisne dekhya kal re bete
Systam sara aj dikha du

#sumitparta #4aadmi #haryanvisong #mahratora

Irumudi Thangi

Kattum Katti

Mandala Poojai

Mandala Viratham

Nadai Thirakkuthu

Sabarimalai Selvoum

Varomappa Ayyappa

These classic Srihari Ayyappan songs capture the essence of the Periya Paadhai pilgrimage through Erumeli, Azutha, Pamba, Pamba Ganapathy Temple, Neelimalai, Sarankuthi, and Sannidhanam.

Also includes contributions from:

Veeramanidasan ‚Äì legendary Ayyappan devotional singer (Irumudi Katti album)

Vashisht Dhupad ‚Äì Srihari‚Äôs son (Nadai Thirakkuthu album)

About the Artist

Over the last 20 years, Srihari has created, conceptualised, and designed several cult classic Ayyappan devotional albums under the Symphony label, including Ayyappanai Thedi, Pathinettu Padi Karuppan Vararu, and Ayyappanai Paadu. His songs remain evergreen favourites among Ayyappa devotees
